high_descs: Walk over to the bed, then turn left and walk up to the wooden end table.
Pick up the rightmost disc off of the end table.
Turn around and walk towards the wall, then hang a right and walk up to the green bin, after that turn right to face the desk.
Put the disc on the wooden desk in front of you.
Walk over to the green bin on the ground to your left.
Pick up the disc out of the green bin.
Turn around and take a step forward, then turn left to face the wooden desk.
Put the disc on the wooden desk behind the set of keys.
anns.task_desc: Move two discs to a wooden desk.

high_descs: Turn to your left and go to the night stand to your left.
Pick up the CD, closest to the bed, on the night stand.
Turn to your left and walk towards the wall, then turn to the desk at your right when you reach the desk chair.
Place the CD on the desk, behind the pen that is in front of the chair.
Turn to the garbage can on the floor to your left.
Remove the CD from the bottom of the garbage bin on the floor.
Turn to your right and go back to the desk.
Place the CD, to the left of the other CD, on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Put two CD's on the desk.

high_descs: Walk to the bed, turn left, and walk to the nightstand.
Pick up the CD on the right.
Turn around, walk halfway across the room, turn right, walk to the trashcan, and turn right to face the desk.
Put the CD on the desk.
Turn around and walk halfway to the door, and turn right to face the trashcan.
Pick up the CD in the trashcan.
Turn right, and walk to the desk.
Put the CD on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Put two CDs on the desk.
